                            <comment id="65308" author="simmonsja" created="Wed, 28 Aug 2013 20:25:25 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Yes the exact problem. I have a patch for it that fixes it. You can close this as a duplicate.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
